'''NVM Express block device''' (<code>CONFIG_BLK_DEV_NVME</code>) needs to be activated:

{{KernelBox|title=linux-4.4|1=
Device Drivers  --->

  ...
  <*> NVM Express block device      
  [*] Open-Channel SSD target support  --->
  ...
}}

It will show up under /dev/nvme*.

